## RanksApi

### Get Rank
## Get Rank
GET https://api.deadlock-api.com/v1/assets/ranks/{{tier}}?language={{language}}&clientVersion={{clientVersion}}
Accept: application/json

### List Ranks
## List Ranks
GET https://api.deadlock-api.com/v1/assets/ranks?language={{language}}&clientVersion={{clientVersion}}
Accept: application/json
